# ⚡ INDEXES (CRITICAL FOR SCALING)

### 1. Trade Sync Index
Used for fast 24h dynamic aggregation.
```sql
CREATE INDEX idx_trades_market_time 
ON trades (market_type, timestamp DESC);
```

### 2. Leaderboard Score Index
Used for near-instant Overall Leaderboard sorting.
```sql
CREATE INDEX idx_leaderboard_score 
ON leaderboard_stats (market_type, score DESC);
```

